body:

本次分享的主题是将 NeMo toolit 工具库与 llama2 大模型以及 Llama index 工具库的结合使用，快速构建中文场景下的检索式对话引擎，本次分享主要面向于对人工智能感兴趣的开发者朋友，通过本次分享您可以获得一下内容：
- LLAMA2 大模型介绍
- Llama index 工具库使用
- Nvidia NeMo toolkit 介绍
- 代码实践：NeMo 结合 Llama2 构建中文检索式对话引擎

Topic Overview:

This session focuses on the integration of the NeMo toolkit with the llama2 large model and Llama index toolkit to swiftly construct a retrieval-based conversational engine in Chinese contexts. It's aimed at developers interested in artificial intelligence. Through this session, you'll gain insights into:
- Introduction to LLAMA2 large models
- Utilization of the Llama index toolkit
-Overview of Nvidia NeMo toolkit
- Code practice: Building a Chinese retrieval-based conversational engine with NeMo and Llama2
